Rating: 3
This was a simple, tasty, healthy weeknight meal. It was flavorful, and I enjoyed the roasted ratatouille so much I may make it independently some time. Now I will admit I did not find the herbes de Provence (and I did swing by a specialty store here in San Francisco), so I improvised and used some oregano and ground fennel. I thought it was lovely regardless. Don't be put off.